    • Method Detail

      • string

        public static String string(int type)
        Converts a TCP/UDP service port number into its textual representation.

      • value

        public static int value(String s)
        Converts a textual representation of a TCP/UDP service into its port number. Integers in the range 0..65535 are also accepted.
        Parameters:
        s - The textual representation of the service.
        Returns:
        The port number, or -1 on error.
